<exercise><p>Convert the following infix expressions to prefix (use full
        parentheses):</p>
    <p><ul>
        <li>(A + B) · ( C + D) · (E + F)</li>
        <li>A + ((B + C) · (D + E))</li>
        <li>A · B · C · D + E + F</li>
    </ul></p>
</exercise>

<exercise><p>Convert the above infix expressions to postfix (use full
