<exercise><p>Evaluate the following postfix expressions. Show the stack as each
        operand and operator is processed.</p>
    <p><ul>
            <li>-  2 3 · 4 +</li>
            <li>1 2 + 3 + 4 + 5 +</li>
            <li>1 2 3 4 5 · + · +</li>
    </ul></p>
</exercise>

